class Solution {
    public ListNode insertionSortList(ListNode head) {
        ListNode dummy = new ListNode(-1, head), curPrev = head, cur = head.next;
        while(cur != null) {
            ListNode jPrev = dummy, j = jPrev.next, curNext = cur.next;
            if(cur.val > curPrev.val) curPrev = cur;
            else {
                while(j.val < cur.val) {
                    jPrev = j; 
                    j = j.next;
                }
                cur.next = j;
                jPrev.next = cur;
                curPrev.next = curNext;
            }
            cur = curNext;
        }
        return dummy.next;
    }
}
```

***Time Complexity :*** <code>O(N<sup>2</sup>)</code>
***Space Complexity :*** `O(1)`, only constant space is being used

